59
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:37,760
Aren't you worried

60
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,400
you'll bring disaster to our family?

61
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:40,640
You little...

62
00:04:40,930 --> 00:04:41,780
Enough.

63
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:45,080
