64
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:46,520
How dare you come here to complain.

65
00:04:46,990 --> 00:04:47,830
I...

66
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,200
What happened with Xiao Jingchu was my fault.

67
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,850
Father, what about Begonia Snow?

68
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,160
She set fire inside Begonia Snow.

69
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:58,400
Do you know who was in there?

70
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,520
How can you even mention this again?

71
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,200
Thanks to Leyao, Qiao'er was saved.

72
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,680
Otherwise, things would be worse.

73
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:13,280
Leyao, step out for now.

74
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,040
Yes, Father.

75
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:32,680
Why fuss with a wild child?

76
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,560
She can't stir up much trouble.

77
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:44,680
Bingqing.

78
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:46,240
This matter...

79
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:48,800
You have truly let me down.

80
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:50,880
Father, I'm sorry.

81
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:53,040
I raised you all by myself.

82
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:55,320
I even feared you'd suffer wrongs.

83
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:57,480
After your mother left us,

84
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,560
I never remarried.

85
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:00,960
Tell me,

86
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:03,640
how I raised you.

87
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:07,440
You've given you all, heart and soul.

88
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:10,480
Louder.

89
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:14,020
You've given you all, heart and soul.

90
00:06:20,100 --> 00:06:24,020
(Spirit tablet of Lady Qin
of the Ning Family)

91
00:06:24,050 --> 00:06:27,480
I gave my all, heart and soul.

92
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,480
Mother, I was wrong.

93
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:38,120
I'll follow your last wishes.

94
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:40,840
Whatever Father asks, I'll do.

95
00:06:58,620 --> 00:06:59,460
Come.

96
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:05,840
In three days,

97
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:09,400
a wealthy merchant from Jiangnan arrives.

98
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:14,000
Serve him well, understand?

99
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:34,920
This is our Ning Family's only hope.

100
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,400
You wretched woman!

101
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:55,040
You've learned to stash money, huh?

102
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:56,680
You can't just take this money.

103
00:07:56,740 --> 00:07:57,580
Give it back to me.

104
00:07:57,580 --> 00:07:58,420
Give it back to you?

105
00:07:58,760 --> 00:08:00,200
You're already mine.

106
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:02,280
Of course, your money is mine too.

107
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,680
My still owes debts to the gambling house.

108
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:14,080
You... how dare you hit me!

109
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,120
I'm your husband.

110
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:18,120
You're truly outrageous.

111
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:19,360
You've struck me for twenty years.

112
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,840
Today, I'll turn the tables on you.

113
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:23,360
Zhao Zhaodi.

114
00:08:23,380 --> 00:08:24,960
I... I want a divorce.

115
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,560
Very well.

116
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,560
Tomorrow at dawn,

117
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:29,280
if I don't get the Divorce Decree,

118
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,240
you'd better watch yourself.

119
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:33,520
You wretched woman.

120
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:36,080
Outrageous indeed!

121
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,680
This place is in the middle of nowhere.

122
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:58,080
Why would the father and daughter

123
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:58,920
come here?

124
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:02,600
Looks like they won't be out soon.

125
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:05,800
We'll have to wait to figure that out.

126
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:10,560
Waiting is fine, but let's find shelter

127
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,040
from the snow first.

128
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:17,840
Follow me.

129
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,440
Didn't expect a young lady like you

130
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:24,880
to know these things.

131
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,640
We village girls

132
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:28,840
