140
00:09:46,640 --> 00:09:47,960
Why would you fear it?

141
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:52,480
Back then, I was just a child.

142
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,040
They used to beat me.

143
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,640
All I could do was hide.

144
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,280
Did you find him yet?

145
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:00,500
Not yet.

146
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:01,480
Hurry and keep searching!

147
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:03,520
- Leave no witnesses!
- Yes.

148
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:04,960
Quickly!

149
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:07,640
Honestly, what a mess.

150
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:08,880
That little rascal.

151
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:11,120
Let's see where you are.

152
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:17,880
Xiao Jingchu.

153
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,440
I've never faced all that.

154
00:10:20,880 --> 00:10:22,720
So I can't say I truly understand,

155
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:24,720
nor do I know how to comfort you.

156
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:28,040
All I can do

157
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:30,120
is simply stay by your side.

158
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:35,000
That's enough for me.

159
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:36,480
What I want

160
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,000
is nothing more than this.

161
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:44,480
Xiao Jingchu, the snow will stop.

162
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:46,480
And the sky

163
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,520
will surely brighten again.

164
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:55,560
Is it warm?

165
00:10:56,870 --> 00:10:57,710
It is.

